==English==

=== Etymology ===
[[French]]: from the past participle of ''[[toucher]]'' (to [[touch]]), from [[Old French]] ''[[tuchier]]''.

=== Interjection ===
'''touché!'''

# {{fencing}} An acknowledgement of a hit.
# An acknowledgement of the success, appropriateness or superiority of an argument.

